{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We Escaped a Twisted Game is a two-player, online co-op escape room game. You and your friend are exploring an abandoned manor when you suddenly find yourselves trapped in a twisted game of survival. Use communication, problem-solving, and teamwork skills to escape\u2014and beware of the evil lurking in the shadows. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524930/extras/MainGif_V5.gif?t=1732686882\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524930/extras/escape_together_new.png?t=1732686882\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>You can't escape alone.</strong> Work together with your partner to progress through the manor. <strong>Communication is key</strong>. Share what you see, but be prepared for your senses to deceive you. <strong>Stay calm</strong> as the clock ticks, the pressure builds, and when you face what lurks in the dark. <strong>Your survival</strong> depends on teamwork, but can you trust each other to the end? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524930/extras/escape_together_gif.gif?t=1732686882\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>PLEASE NOTE:</strong> This escape can only be played in co-op. Each player needs their own device and game copy to play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524930/extras/two_Stories_one_escape.png?t=1732686882\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take on the roles of Chad and Stacy, each navigating different parts of the manor. Two distinct paths, but one shared goal: escape together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524930/extras/chad_stacy_gif.gif?t=1732686882\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524930/extras/15_challenging_rooms.png?t=1732686882\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover 15 unique rooms, each featuring its own theme, puzzles, and challenges. Dive into a mix of intense brain-teasers, creepy corridors, and teamwork-driven tasks that will put your skills and trust to the test.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524930/extras/15_themed_rooms_gif.gif?t=1732686882\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524930/extras/you_are_not_alone.png?t=1732686882\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Something is watching you. Stay alert, trust each other, and survive together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524930/extras/evil_lives_here_gif.gif?t=1732686882\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524930/extras/multiplayer_options.png?t=1732686882\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Public lobbies for solo players.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Private lobbies for friends.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In-game voicechat.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524930/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732686882","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524930/page.bg.jpg?t=1732686882","capsule_image":"https://shar